### get all
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders

## get by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/1

### get by user id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/search/customer?customer=101

### get by date range
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/search/date?start=2024-01-01&end=2024-12-31

### get by advisor id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/search/advisor?advisor=2

### get by mechanic id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/search/mechanic?mechanic=4

### get by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders/search/status?status=COMPLETED

